OL,3,CMan sentenced for one punch pub murder
OL,5,FA man has been jailed for life after
OL,6,Fhe killed a "timid, fun-loving man"
OL,7,Fwith a single punch from behind
OL,8,Foutside a pub in Swansea.
OL,10,FChristopher Cooper, 39, punched Kelvin
OL,11,FEvans once to the head outside The
OL,12,FStation Hotel, Gorseinon on May 26
OL,13,Flast year after feeling "slighted"
OL,14,Fover his partner's karaoke singing.
OL,16,FMr Evans was immediately knocked
OL,17,Funconscious and was taken to hospital,
OL,18,Fwhere he died a month later.
