OL,3,CMan sentenced for one punch pub murder
OL,5,FAfter the incident, Cooper boasted
OL,6,Fabout the attack, branding his fists
OL,7,Fhis "bad boys".
OL,9,FCooper, from the Maritime Quarter,
OL,10,FSwansea, was sentenced to life with a
OL,11,Fminimum term of 16 years for murder at
OL,12,FSwansea Crown Court on Friday.
OL,14,FCooper's partner, 54-year-old
OL,15,FCatherine Tracy Francis, from
OL,16,FLlanelli, was also found guilty of
OL,17,Fassisting an offender and sentenced to
OL,18,Ftwo years in jail.
