OL,3,CMan sentenced for one punch pub murder
OL,5,FFollowing the sentencing, Cooper
OL,6,Fshouted at Judge Geraint Walters as he
OL,7,Fwas escorted from the courtroom.
OL,9,FHe said: "Go f*** yourself ` how's
OL,10,Fthat. You're a d***head."
OL,12,FThe court heard that Mr Evans, 64, had
OL,13,Fbeen drinking at the Station Hotel,
OL,14,Fknown locally as "The Gyp" in May last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FCooper, who was drinking there with
OL,18,FFrancis, followed Mr Evans as he left
OL,19,Fto meet his partner at another pub
OL,20,Fwhen he punched him once in the head
OL,21,Ffrom behind.
