OL,3,CMan sentenced for one punch pub murder
OL,5,FThe judge said Cooper appeared to have
OL,6,Ffelt "slighted" after Mr Evans and his
OL,7,Fpartner had shared a look while
OL,8,FFrancis was singing karaoke.
OL,10,FFrancis was aware of the assault but
OL,11,Fdid not call the police and analysis
OL,12,Fof her phone showed that she had
OL,13,Fsearched for hotels immediately after
OL,14,Fthe attack and the pair had packed a
OL,15,Fcar to leave the area.
OL,17,FPolice arrested them the next day at a
OL,18,Fservice station in South Cornelly.
