OL,3,CMan sentenced for one punch pub murder
OL,5,FAddressing Cooper, Judge Walters said:
OL,6,F"Your victim, Kelvin Evans, was a much-
OL,7,Floved member of the Evans family and
OL,8,Fthe wider community.
OL,10,F"A man without an angry bone in his
OL,11,Fbody. A timid, fun-loving family man
OL,12,Fadmired by all."
OL,14,FHe added: "It was a cowardly punch,
OL,15,Fdelivered from behind, totally
OL,16,Funexpected and one, inevitably, that
OL,17,Fwould result in really serious injury
OL,18,Fif the head were to strike a hard
OL,19,Fsurface.
