OL,5,F"The motive for this violence was the
OL,6,Fperceived feeling that your partner,
OL,7,FTracy Francis, had been slighted by Mr
OL,8,FEvans and his partner simply looking
OL,9,Fat each other, and saying something,
OL,10,Fwhich you had perceived to be about
OL,11,FTracy Francis' voice as she used the
OL,12,Fkaraoke machine.
OL,14,F"It festered in your mind from that
OL,15,Fmoment onwards and that was enough to
OL,16,Ftrigger an attempt to cause really
OL,17,Fserious bodily harm ` as an act
OL,18,Feffectively of revenge.
