OL,5,F"Nobody was going to slight you, or
OL,6,Fanybody connected with you without
OL,7,Fpaying the price for it."
OL,9,FThe judge said he believed Cooper had
OL,10,Fwaited for Mr Evans to leave before he
OL,11,Ffollowed him out and would have struck
OL,12,Fhim again if his victim had not fallen
OL,13,Fto the floor.
OL,15,FHe said it was "chilling" that Cooper
OL,16,Fhad then boasted about the attack,
OL,17,Fcalling his fists "these bad boys" and
OL,18,Fappeared to show no remorse during the
OL,19,Ftrial.
