OL,5,FCooper had pleaded guilty to
OL,6,Fmanslaughter but denied murder, but he
OL,7,Fwas convicted by a jury after a two-
OL,8,Fweek trial.
OL,10,FFrancis pleaded not guilty to
OL,11,Fassisting an offender but was also
OL,12,Fconvicted by the jury.
OL,14,FMr Evan's 92-year-old mother, Maureen
OL,15,FEvans, stood in the dock and faced her
OL,16,Fson's killer as she gave an impact
OL,17,Fstatement, holding back tears as she
OL,18,Fspoke about losing her son.
