OL,5,F"You never as a mother expect your
OL,6,Fchildren to go before you, I thought
OL,7,Fat the age of 92, all my children
OL,8,Fwould be there when my time came," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"Kelvin was so helpful and one of the
OL,12,Fbest sons you could wish for.
OL,14,F"I look at his picture every night and
OL,15,Fevery morning when I wake up, I miss
OL,16,Fhim so much."
OL,18,FIn statements read to the court, Mr
OL,19,FEvan's family described him as "kind,
OL,20,Ffunny and loved by all who knew him".
