OL,5,FJanet Cross, Mr Evan's ex-partner,
OL,6,Fsaid they had previously planned to
OL,7,Fretire to Sicily, and she wished they
OL,8,Fhad done that before last May.
OL,10,FShe said: "The thought that Kelvin is
OL,11,Fno longer with me is simply
OL,12,Fheartbreaking.
OL,14,F"Kelvin was the love of my life and
OL,15,Fwas in my life and the lives of my two
OL,16,Fchildren for 25 years.
OL,18,F"Not only was he a second dad, he was
OL,19,Ftheir friend."
