OL,5,FShe added: "The murder of Kelvin has
OL,6,Fleft me with horrendous nightmares,
OL,7,Fsleepless nights and days and nights
OL,8,Ffilled with inconsolable grief.
OL,10,F"To add to the hurt, I have had to sit
OL,11,Fin court and listen to the lies told
OL,12,Fby the defendants.
OL,14,F"Both appear to be utterly devoid of
OL,15,Fempathy or emotion for what happened
OL,16,Fto Kelvin as a result of their actions.
OL,18,F"Christopher Cooper can only be
OL,19,Fdescribed as walking rage ` he not
OL,20,Fonly killed Kelvin, but he killed a
OL,21,Fpart of me too."
