OL,5,FNia Sturgess of the Crown Prosecution
OL,6,FService said: "This case shows the
OL,7,Fdevastating consequences that can
OL,8,Farise from just one punch.
OL,10,F"What started as a trivial issue for
OL,11,FChristopher Cooper resulted in a
OL,12,Fsenseless act of violence and a tragic
OL,13,Floss of life.
OL,15,F"Cooper punched Kelvin Evans from
OL,16,Fbehind, giving him no opportunity to
OL,17,Fdefend himself.
